01:09:08.920 --> 01:09:10.760
Trust me. This will work.

01:09:11.120 --> 01:09:12.040
Okay.

01:09:12.279 --> 01:09:13.000
Now, we wait.

01:09:13.439 --> 01:09:15.080
- Qin, this way. Come on!
- "Will you be my partner?"

01:09:15.120 --> 01:09:16.260
- Quickly!
- And smile!

01:09:16.479 --> 01:09:17.279
Qin!

01:09:24.479 --> 01:09:25.760
Surprise!

01:09:26.200 --> 01:09:27.080
Yoo-hoo!

01:09:30.600 --> 01:09:31.439
Why are you giving me this?

01:09:33.600 --> 01:09:35.319
Oh, and...

01:09:36.840 --> 01:09:38.000
You're not going to accept it?

01:09:38.439 --> 01:09:39.040
Yoo-hoo!

01:09:39.080 --> 01:09:39.880
Please accept it.

01:09:39.920 --> 01:09:41.640
Accept it! Accept it!

01:09:41.680 --> 01:09:42.840
Accept it!

01:09:43.399 --> 01:09:44.279
Will you be my partner?

01:09:57.200 --> 01:09:58.680
My friend's in a whole different league.

01:09:58.920 --> 01:09:59.920
Gosh, that was sweet.

01:09:59.960 --> 01:10:00.960
You and your words.

01:10:01.320 --> 01:10:02.160
I'll see you in a bit.

01:10:02.200 --> 01:10:02.880
- Oh?
- Qin!

01:10:02.920 --> 01:10:04.000
- Where is he going?
- What about us?

01:10:04.040 --> 01:10:05.040
Do we have to follow him?

01:10:05.160 --> 01:10:05.880
Of course.

01:10:06.160 --> 01:10:07.560
Go follow them!

01:10:17.680 --> 01:10:19.080
Mm. Can I go now?

01:10:20.380 --> 01:10:21.780
We can't just talk nicely to each other?

01:10:23.160 --> 01:10:24.440
How is this not talking nicely?

01:10:26.480 --> 01:10:27.920
So he's your boyfriend, correct?

01:10:31.040 --> 01:10:32.160
What's that got to do with you?

01:10:33.200 --> 01:10:34.600
Can you just give me a clear answer?

01:10:35.520 --> 01:10:37.320
I'm trying to be nice here.

01:10:38.200 --> 01:10:39.520
Duang is not just a friend. That's all.

01:10:42.300 --> 01:10:43.120
Qin!

01:10:54.800 --> 01:10:55.800
Do you want to go home now?

01:10:57.760 --> 01:10:58.520
Mm.

01:11:04.320 --> 01:11:05.320
Let's leave.

01:13:10.620 --> 01:13:11.940
You're not going to ask me anything?

01:13:21.640 --> 01:13:22.920
You two were friends?

01:13:26.380 --> 01:13:27.380
Just friends.

01:13:29.860 --> 01:13:31.660
But he thought of me more than that.

01:13:40.000 --> 01:13:42.000
We weren't really

01:13:44.120 --> 01:13:45.120
in the talking stage, either.

01:14:50.520 --> 01:14:52.520
You haven't talked to him since then?

01:14:54.200 --> 01:14:55.080
Mm.

01:14:57.400 --> 01:14:59.240
When he confessed how he felt about me,

01:15:02.160 --> 01:15:04.160
I simply told him
I had good feelings toward him.

01:15:06.440 --> 01:15:08.840
But I didn't want
to advance the relationship.

01:15:11.760 --> 01:15:13.640
Since then, we rarely talked,

01:15:16.600 --> 01:15:18.160
even though prior to this,

01:15:19.740 --> 01:15:21.140
we were always at each other's side.

01:15:26.300 --> 01:15:27.300
Was I a mean person?

01:15:30.240 --> 01:15:31.120
You were.

01:15:36.880 --> 01:15:39.200
But I never thought of you as a friend.

01:15:46.600 --> 01:15:49.600
We agreed we'd be each other's partner.

01:16:55.280 --> 01:16:56.440
You're still upset?

01:16:57.120 --> 01:16:58.080
Who the hell are you?

01:16:58.120 --> 01:16:59.280
I don't know who this is.

01:16:59.320 --> 01:17:00.600
Duang that I know

01:17:00.640 --> 01:17:01.840
always fights till the end.

01:17:01.880 --> 01:17:03.240
Jamie asked if we wanted to drink.

01:17:03.440 --> 01:17:04.040
Sure.

01:17:04.240 --> 01:17:05.240
Can I borrow Qin for a bit?

01:17:05.800 --> 01:17:06.520
Oh.

01:17:07.480 --> 01:17:08.480
I'm not here to borrow him.

01:17:09.520 --> 01:17:10.520
I'm here to take him back.

01:17:10.560 --> 01:17:12.080
The guy's cheeky, alright?

01:17:12.400 --> 01:17:13.400
I trust Qin,

01:17:13.640 --> 01:17:14.640
but not that bastard.

01:17:14.800 --> 01:17:15.560
Care for a game?

01:17:15.720 --> 01:17:17.360
The game's called "Heart Rate."

01:17:17.400 --> 01:17:18.720
The teddy I gave you...

01:17:19.520 --> 01:17:20.680
You still hold onto it, don't you?

